            <title>[HBASE-6732] [89-fb] Reduce scope of synchronized block in HBaseClient.Connection#sendParam.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-6732</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;sendParam method synchronizes on out stream (so that only one thread writes to socket).  Right now it prepares (eg. compress) message under this lock as well. Lock should be taken only for sending.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
